<li id="cite_note-ODCC_self-27"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-ODCC_self_27-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">"Sermon on the Mount." Cross, F. L., ed. <i>The Oxford Dictionary of the Christian Church</i>. New York: Oxford University Press. 2005</span>
