<li id="cite_note-43"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-43">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">See: <i><a href="/wiki/Martyrdom" class="mw-redirect" title="Martyrdom">Martyrdom</a></i></span>
